content:
Surprisingly disappointing.
1 - The first episodes begin presenting characters that we will never see in anime;
2 - The director tries to create suspense that does not work around these same characters presented at the beginning of the anime and that we will never see in the anime again;
3 - Where are the characters presented at the beginning of the anime?
4 - The episodes of the "Lizardmen" were annoying, boring and uninteresting;
5 - I was expecting more focus on the main characters and the anime wrapped me around nine apisodes where nothing happened with characters that I can not even remember who they were.
I watched untilthe end in the hope that it would improve, unfortunately that was not the case.
